  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.8.10">
<l>nātaṉ ñālaṅkoḷ</l>
<l>pāta ṉeṉṉammā</l>
<l>ṉōtam pōlkiḷar</l>
<l>vēta nīraṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The lord, the one with feet</l>
<l>that took the world, my father,</l>
<l>has water [colour] like the sea</l>
<l>[and] the nature of the shining Veda.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
